    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine starts and runs fine, but you may notice some minor leaks and a bit of hesitation during acceleration. The exterior has several visible scratches and some fading paint on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for transportation at a lower price point, provided they are comfortable with some cosmetic flaws and the potential for minor repairs in the near future.",
