    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and still runs like a total charm! It\u2019s in great shape overall and has plenty of life left in it for all your upcoming adventures. It\u2019s clean, comfy, and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve loved driving this car, and I know you will too\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
