    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted E92 M3, powered by the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant features individual throttle bodies and is paired with the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission for seamless torque delivery. The vehicle has been maintained with technical rigor, including documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis dynamics remain sharp, supported by the M Variable Differential Lock and EDC-equipped suspension. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the performance remains uncompromising, delivering linear power all the way to its 8,400 RPM redline. A turn-key example for the driver who prioritizes mechanical integrity and engineering pedigree.",
